---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import BodyContent from "../components/BodyContent.astro";
import SectionContainer from "../components/SectionContainer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Play Vire | Grand Strategy Game that is opensource, free, and lots of fun"
  description="Vire is actively building a community around creating a grand strategy game with endless content and endless fun."
>
  <BodyContent>
    <SectionContainer>
      <h1 class="text-2xl">What is Vire?</h1>
      <h2 class="text-xl">TL;DR</h2>
      <p>
        Vire is an open-source, 2D grand strategy game where you can either
        conquer the world - or build your own.
      </p>
      <ul class="pl-4 list-disc ml-4">
        <li>Play historical or fictional scenarios</li>
        <li>Create your own with a powerful in-game editor</li>
        <li>Share content with the community</li>
      </ul>
      <h2 class="text-xl">
        Simple Grand Strategy Game Focused on Customization and Community
      </h2>
      <ul class="pl-4 list-disc ml-4">
        <li>Play deep, strategic scenarios - or invent your own</li>
        <li>
          Use an intuitive editor to create nations, maps, tech trees, units,
          and more.
        </li>
        <li>Share your creations in the public content library</li>
        <li>Play solo or multiplayer.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Whether you're into alernate history, fantasy worldbuilding or just
        painting the map your favorite color - Vire gives you to the tools to
        make it happen.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-xl">Features</h2>
      <h3>Classic Grand Strategy Systems</h3>
      <ul class="pl-4 list-disc ml-4">
        <li>Diplomacy, Economy, Military, Research</li>
        <li>
          Create alliances, build tech trees, and lead your people to victory
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-lg">AI & Modding</h3>
      <ul class="pl-4 list-disc ml-4">
        <li>Built-in behavior trees</li>
        <li>Advanced users can script thier own AI logic.</li>
        <li>Open source means full control.</li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-lg">Flexible Combat & Units</h3>
      <ul class="pl-4 list-disc ml-4">
        <li>
          Customize unit types (e.g., swordsmen, mechs, dragons, or space
          marines).
        </li>
        <li>Define damage types like pierce, hack, magic, etc.</li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-lg">Deep Resource & Economy Management</h3>
      <ul class="pl-4 list-disc ml-4">
        <li>Add jobs, buildings and simulate population growth.</li>
        <li>Create complex economies with custom resource types.</li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-lg">Multiplayer & Sharing</h3>
      <ul class="pl-4 list-disc ml-4">
        <li>Play single-player against custom AI.</li>
        <li>Or host/join multiplayer games through our free server.</li>
        <li>Share your creations in the content library.</li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-lg">Development</h3>
      <p>Vire is in early development</p>
      <p>You can follow progress through monthly devlogs on this site</p>
      <ul class="pl-4 list-disc ml-4">
        <li>Source code is available on GitHub</li>
        <li>Community builds will be published here once they're stable.</li>
        <li>Full roadmap and changelog coming soon.</li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-lg">Community</h3>
      <p>
        We're building more than a game â€” we're building a space for
        collaboration and creativity.
      </p>
      <ul class="pl-4 list-disc ml-4">
        <li>
          Join the <a
            class="text-blue-600 underline"
            href="https://discord.gg/t59hty7T"
            rel="noopener noreferrer">Discord</a
          > to share feedback, ideas, and memes.
        </li>
        <li>Submit your own scenarios or play others'.</li>
        <li>Help shape hte future of the game.</li>
      </ul>
    </SectionContainer>
  </BodyContent>
</Layout>
